== Algorithms to be implemented (in order of interest) ==
- Smoothsort ( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smoothsort )
- Gnome sort ( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gnome_sort )
- Merge sort that uses insertion sort when sorting < k elements.
- Quicksort that uses insertion sort when sorting < k elements.
- Timsort ( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timsort )
- Comb sort ( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comb_sort )
- Odd-even sort ( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odd-even_sort )
